Announcing the release of a free constraint solver:

Cassowary Constraint Solver for Smalltalk, C++, and Java
Version 0.1

Alan Borning <borning@cs.washington.edu> and
Greg J. Badros <gjb@cs.washington.edu>
University of Washington
Computer Science and Engineering
19-June-1998

with Constraint Drawing Applet (CDA) by Michael Noth <noth@cs.washington.edu>

http://www.cs.washington.edu/research/constraints/cassowary

Contact: cassowary@cs.washington.edu


Cassowary is a constraint solving toolkit which efficiently solves
systems of linear equalities and inequalities.
